[SniperRifle]
; EN: Description="The Lightning Gun is a high-power energy rifle capable of ablating even the heaviest carapace armor. Acquisition of a target at long range requires a steady hand, but the anti-jitter effect of the optical system reduces the weapon's learning curve significantly. Once the target has been acquired, the operator depresses the trigger, painting a proton 'patch' on the target. Milliseconds later the rifle emits a high voltage arc of electricity, which seeks out the charge differential and annihilates the target."
Description="Pistolet BŇāyskawicowy to karabin o duŇľej mocy, zdolny do zniszczenia nawet najcińôŇľszego pancerza pancerza. Namierzenie celu z duŇľej odlegŇāoŇõci wymaga pewnej rńôki, ale efekt anty-jitter systemu optycznego znacznie zmniejsza krzywńÖ uczenia sińô broni. Po osińÖgnińôciu celu operator naciska spust, malujńÖc na nim protonowńÖ ‚ÄěŇāatkńô‚ÄĚ. Milisekundy p√≥Ňļniej karabin emituje Ňāuk elektryczny o wysokim napińôciu, kt√≥ry wyszukuje r√≥Ňľnicńô Ňāadunk√≥w i unicestwia cel."
; EN: ItemName="Lightning Gun"
ItemName="Piorun piorunowy"

